quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  15,45,"Mu by’ukuri,abatinya Allah bazaba bari mu busitani (Ijuru) butembamo imigezi"
  15,46,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Nimuryinjiremo mu mahoro kandi mutekanye"
  15,47,"Tuzanakura inzika mu bituza byabo (nuko babane mu ijuru) nk’abavandimwe, bari ku bitanda berekeranye (baganira bishimye)"
  15,48,Ntibazigera barigiramo umunaniro kandi ntibazarivanwamo
  15,49,"(Yewe Muhamadi) bwira abagaragu banjye ko mu by’ukuri, ndi Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimbabazi"
  15,50,Kandi ko n’ibihano byanjye ari ibihano bibabaza cyane
  15,51,Unababarire inkuru y’abashyitsi (abamalayika) ba Aburahamu
  15,52,"Ubwo binjiraga iwe bakavuga bati \"Salamu (amahoro)\" , (nuko akabikiriza) maze akavuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, muduteye ubwoba"
  15,53,"Baravuga bati \"Ntugire ubwoba! Mu by’ukuri, tuje kuguha inkuru nziza (yo kuzabyara) umuhungu w’umunyabwenge"
  15,54,"(Aburahamu) aravuga ati \"Ese murampa inkuru nziza (yo kuzabyara umuhungu) kandi ngeze mu zabukuru? Iyo nkuru nziza ni bwoko ki"
  15,55,"Baravuga bati \"Tuguhaye inkuru nziza y’ukuri. Bityo, reka kuba mu bihebye"
  15,56,"(Aburahamu) aravuga ati \"Nonese ni nde wakwiheba mu mpuhwe za Nyagasani we, usibye abayobye"
  15,57,"(Aburahamu arongera) aravuga ati \"Ni iki kibagenza yemwe mwa ntumwa mwe"
  15,58,"Baravuga bati \"Mu by’ukuri, twoherejwe ku bantu b’inkozi z’ibibi (ngo tubarimbure)"
  15,59,"Usibye gusa umuryango wa Lutwi (Loti). Mu by’ukuri, turabarokora bose"
  15,60,Uretse umugore we (wigometse) twagennye ko aba mu bazasigara inyuma (bakarimbuka)